reviews.text: Very good quality hotel. Good service and very good breakfast offer and variety. Sauna and indoor swimming pool opened till 10pm
Excellent hotel with great location. Perfect service and very good food. Vry wide selection for the breakfast. A bit expensive but this can be justified by its quality.
Comfortable rooms. Great location. Nice SPA
Excellent place. Convenient location. Very helpful and attentive staff.
In brief: the location is fab, facilities are good and staff is friendly, but … let’s put it this way: it is the service that leads to the assessment of three stars only.
